                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9004" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0411</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1470 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">不负青山不负人：佛坪县林业局的“绿富”乡村振兴路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Live up to the expectations of environment and folk: Foping County Forestry Bureau’s “Green Wealth”&#160;rural revitalization journey</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">姚利丽，王军智，张宇驰，姚远，吴烨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北农林科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">佛坪林业局</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共管理和社会组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行政部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">林长制；学习型组织；圣吉学习型组织模型；利益联结机制；组织激励与约束</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Forest chief system, Learning organization, Senge Learning organization model, Benefit Linkage Mechanism, Organizational Incentives and Constraints</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以春、夏、秋、冬为时序描述了2023年佛坪林业局以创建学习型组织为抓手，秉承“不负青山不负人”的理念，通过基于本地资源禀赋，结合工作实际，部署阶段性的工作重点，走出了一条“绿富”乡村振兴路。案例中，佛坪林业局以构建学习型组织迎接时代的挑战，春、夏、秋、冬四季不间断地进行工作一线“干中学”，铸牢基础“常态学”，巩固提升“互动学”，突出重点“集中学”。通过推进学习型机关建设，发展绿色经济，提高机关效能。而学习型机关建设，对于实现机关现代化，促进学习型社会建设，加快社会现代化步伐，构建社会主义和谐社会，具有重要的意义。本案例的开发旨在引导学员理解和掌握组织行为学的学习型组织概念内涵及模型，培养学员的管理者思维；引导学员关注乡村振兴、共同富裕、林长制等重要国策，增加学员对国情的了解，提升学员对“国之大者”的认知。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case is descriptive, with 2023 spring, summer, autumn, and winter in chronological order. The Foping forestry administration took the creation of a learning organization as its starting point, adopted the concept of “Living up to the expectations of the environment and people,” and “China Communist Party red” empowers “Ecological green,” deploying a focus on spring, summer, autumn, and winter four seasons work, and achieved favored deliverables, leading the local people to a “Green rich” rural revitalization road. In the case study, the Foping Forestry Bureau embraces the challenge of the times by building a learning organization, continuously engaging in “learning by doing” throughout the spring, summer, autumn, and winter seasons. They solidify their foundation with “normal learning,”enhance and improve with “interactive learning,” and focus on critical points with “concentrated learning.”By promoting the construction of a learning-oriented agency, they develop a green economy and improve the efficiency of the agency. The construction of a learning-oriented agency is of great significance for achieving the agency’s modernization, promoting the construction of a learning society, accelerating the pace of social modernization, and building a harmonious socialist society. The development of this case aims to guide students in understanding and mastering the connotation and model of the learning organization in organizational behavior, as well as cultivating students’ managerial thinking. It also aims to guide students to pay attention to important national policies such as rural revitalization, common prosperity, and forest chief systems, increase students’ understanding of the national conditions, and enhance students’ awareness of the“Country&#39;s priority.”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《领导力与团队管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">学习型组织；圣吉学习型组织模型；学习型组织模型五要素</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
